Interface VerticalNavigationOverflow

    VerticalNavigationOverflowImpl
    public interface VerticalNavigationOverflow
extends utam.core.framework.base.PageObject
    Selector: lightning-vertical-navigation-overflow. Represents the lightning-vertical-navigation-overflow Lightning web component. Get the item count. Check if it's expanded or toggle the section. Get all the vertical navigation items, get the active item, an item by name or an item by index. , created from JSON resources/utam/force/verticalNavigationOverflow.utam.json
